@{line}
@{b}@{fg shine}Package Contents@{fg text}@{ub}@{line}
@{b}@{fg shine}================@{fg text}@{ub}@{par}

This package consists of:@{par}
@{code}
  ScreenMaster               GUI for ScreenDaemon.
